# 14. Rendering System

Rendering uses the HTML Canvas API.

Objects are drawn using:

ctx.drawImage()

Draw order is very important.

Rendering order:

1 Background  
2 Platforms  
3 Buttons  
4 Doors  
5 Players  
6 UI

Incorrect ordering can cause objects to appear in front of others incorrectly.

